Debug messages can be found if you launch rl from the terminal

Running
==
Linux only game as the directory searching code is using dirent to look for
creature definitions.

To run you must create a folder called img and put an image
called tileset.png into it.

tileset.png has a very specific format as described below:
- 16x5 image made of tiles
- each tile is 64x64
- the characters are noted in textures/textures.h
